WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.640
South Africans await President

00:00:01.640 --> 00:00:04.000
Ramaphosa to announce the election date.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.360
The Home Affairs Department says its officers will

00:00:06.360 --> 00:00:09.780
from today extend their operations by two hours.

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:11.600
This is to accommodate the I. C.

00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:13.920
Second and final voter registration drive

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:15.740
that is happening this weekend.

00:00:15.840 --> 00:00:17.840
Illegible voters will also use the

00:00:17.840 --> 00:00:20.500
opportunity to update or change their details

00:00:20.520 --> 00:00:22.320
before the voters role is closed

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:24.900
before the 2024 general elections.

00:00:25.040 --> 00:00:27.640
Now department says it will also set up mobile

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:30.940
offices in areas that require additional support.
